Subject: [RECONSTRUCTION] Use the published local core snapshot

This experimental patch substitutes the inaccessible tivi.io/core pseudo-version
with the root core/ module published in the fixed IVXV tree. It is not claimed
to reproduce the KOV2025 dependency: no public evidence proves byte equivalence,
and the patch changes module resolution semantics.

diff --git a/common/collector/go.mod b/common/collector/go.mod
--- a/common/collector/go.mod
+++ b/common/collector/go.mod
@@ -29,0 +30,2 @@
+
+replace tivi.io/core => ../../core
diff --git a/voting/go.mod b/voting/go.mod
--- a/voting/go.mod
+++ b/voting/go.mod
@@ -35,0 +36,2 @@
+
+replace tivi.io/core => ../core
